channel.title: Akyut - Bones (James Lucien's Epic :b:️oneless Mix
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/james-lucien-official/akyut-bones-james-luciens-epic-mix
The third one. It's never as good as the original or the sequel, but they still made it anyway to cash in on the success of the original, destroying what little good faith the audience has left in the franchise.
![image|445x312](upload://89Kh4C2qNmP4QVFSNaeKySIVXZ7.png)
This is entering the new competitions channel on the [Auxy Community Discord Server](https://discord.gg/7yguA4S). Special thanks to @Akyut for hosting it. I hope I won ;3
[details="The realization of what I was doing ;3"] ![image|446x451](upload://yvCdAZ1TRqb3vnAjvXsRLFqm443.png) [/details]
I know I said I was out of upload minutes as James Lucien. Well, I cleared out some old remixes that I didn't want anymore and I made some room. I think it was a wise choice. The Epic trilogy is complete.
![image|500x500](upload://iRrf5s0vFwFYhQuKfzGw0Z2H5CA.jpg)
